title: Windows 10 KB3176927 Cumulative Update x64
description:
This is the .cab update file for Windows Insiders who are on the 14393 build. 14393 is the RTM version for the Windows 10 Anniversary Update which will release publicly to consumers on August 2nd, 2016.

Instructions to Install this .cab file:

1: Open CMD with Admin privileges.
2: Type in this command - DISM.exe /Online /Add-Package /PackagePath:(path to .cab file)
NOTE: Replace (path to .cab file) with the directory to the .cab file.
3: Reboot
